latestPosts.caption:
Learning how to pause and romanticise every little detail💛
@lheritage_bistro 📍Mosman

Still not over how this restaurant - it completely blew me away✨ Every detail - from the flavors to the creativity on the plate, it was all perfection. It felt like I was in Paris in this most dreamy and magical restaurant where every corner was thoughtfully curated.

What we got: 
🍸 Lychee martini
🦪 Oysters in this most delicious sauce
🍣 Fish of the day which was this delicious Tuna seared on each side 
🫛 Green beans cooked in yummy buttery garlic sauce 
🍆Ratatouille serving up the yummiest veggies 
🥩 The most delicious steak with crunchy chippies 
🍮 Crème brûlée which was caramel perfection 
🍫 Fondant au chocolat that oozed out with chocolate sauce that melted in your mouth
